mean_cn: phr. 留存收益，留存盈利
mean_en: any after-tax profit that is reinvested in the firm rather than being paid out to the owners of the company in dividends
sentence: At the annual profit sharing, the company reserved some retained profit for future investment.
sentence_trans: 在年底分红时，公司保留了一部分留存收益以便在未来进行投资。
